    "errors, conflated values from different capture formats, or values that were themselves",
    "estimated in their original source.",
    "",
    "DO NOT use hFOVDegrees values in production calculations until each entry has been",
    "verified by AT LEAST ONE of the following methods:",
    "  (a) Direct measurement on physical hardware via AVCaptureDevice.activeFormat.videoFieldOfView,",
    "  (b) Confirmation against a minimum of 3 independent, citable published sources",
    "      (e.g. iFixit teardown measurements, Apple developer documentation, peer-reviewed technical analysis).",
    "",
    "When a value is verified, set hFOVVerified to true and update hFOVSource to describe",
    "the verification method used (e.g. 'measured on device — AVFoundation videoFieldOfView').",
    "",
    "The hFOVSource field describes how the current estimate was derived — it does NOT",
    "indicate the value has been confirmed. All entries start with hFOVVerified: false.",
    "",
    "modelIdentifiers for M4 iPad Pro and M2 iPad Air entries are also unverified and",
    "should be confirmed against a physical device or the Apple model identifier registry."
  ],
